java.lang.Object
  binaryTree.ArrayListCompleteBinaryTree<E>
Type Parameters:
E - the element type.
All Implemented Interfaces:
BinaryTree<E>, CompleteBinaryTree<E>, java.lang.Iterable<E>, Tree<E>
public class ArrayListCompleteBinaryTree<E>
extends java.lang.Object
implements CompleteBinaryTree<E>

The ArrayListCompleteBinaryTree implements CompleteBinaryTree interface. When an ArrayListCompleteBinaryTree is first created, it contains no items.

1.0
